From 9243ed16503521b5f254b9e00cddc0600a47d3d9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sat, 19 Jul 2025 00:39:12 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] ath12k-wifi7-extn: Add minimal code to integrate 240Mhz extensions with ath12k-wifi7

Integrate the below 240MHz support in ath12k_wifi7 to use the
extension APIs:

Add structure ath12k_ops_wifi7_extn, which links the function pointers to
extension functions. The API ath12k_wifi7_hw_init_extn initialises this
structure.
This add support for driver_ops_extn similar to the driver_ops in ath12K.
This is useful to get the ath12k extn information from mac80211 component
using function pointers.

Signed-off-by: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Venkateswara Swamy Bandaru <vbandaru@qti.qualcomm.com>

---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c     | 6 ++++++
 1 files changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
index 7763895..4b3796e 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hw.c
@@ -14,6 +14,7 @@
 #include "ce.h"
 #include "../hw.h"
 #include "hw.h"
+#include "../qcn_extns/ath12k_cmn_extn.h"
 #include "../mhi.h"
 #include "mhi.h"
 #include "dp_rx.h"
@@ -1732,6 +1735,8 @@ int ath12k_wifi7_hw_init(struct ath12k_base *ab)
 		ab->hw_params = hw_params;
 	}
 	ab->ath12k_ops = &ath12k_ops_wifi7;
+
+	ath12k_wifi7_hw_init_extn(ab);
 
 	ath12k_info(ab, "WiFi7 Hardware name: %s\n", ab->hw_params->name);
 
-- 
